      "review_summary": "This PR adds Claude web timeout validation, deadline handling, CLI auto fallback/cancellation behavior, Linux gating, and focused deadline/fallback tests.\n\nReproducibility: no. live high-confidence provider reproduction was run because AGENTS.md warns against Keychain and browser-cookie probes. Source inspection does reproduce the remaining merge concern: app-auto web availability and fetch each receive a fresh full timeout.",
